                        </h4>
                        <div class="attribute-value">
                            <input type="text" name="system.recursos.terciario.value" value="{{system.recursos.terciario.value}}" placeholder="0" data-dtype="Number" style="border-bottom: 1px solid purple;">
                            <span class="sep"> / </span>
                            <input type="text" name="system.recursos.terciario.max" value="{{system.recursos.terciario.max}}" placeholder="0" data-dtype="Number" style="border-bottom: 1px solid purple;">                            
